S

score(String) - Static method in class com.qrhunter.ScoringSystem
Calculates the score of a qr code using its SHA-256 sum The score is based on how many repeats of a specific character there are Repeated 0s in a row are worth 20^(n-1) points For other repeated "m" hex values, they are worth m^(n-1) points
